data.description: Gorgeous townhome with low maintenance living in a quaint community ready for new owners!  Large Kitchen features premier 42" craftsman cabinetry, gorgeous stainless steel appliances and granite countertops.  Upgraded engineered hardwood floors throughout the first floor to include nine foot ceilings with formal dining room and a family room with cozy fireplace.  Spacious bedrooms each with ceiling fans and big closets. Large EnSuite with his & hers closets and private bath.  Designated and overflow parking available. Portlock Square homes is a limited number of townhome style condos quietly tucked away in the metropolitan area of Hampton Roads.  Sellers VA loan is also assumable at an impressive 3%. Come see!
